gov.usgs.comcat

Class SimplePick

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.comcat.SimplePick

  • public class SimplePick
extends java.lang.Object
    This class just holds the simple stuff for a pick. It is used in the ComCatEvent class to build up a list of picks from the QuakeML file.
